{"tid":1696580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"調查發現：僅29%受訪加拿大人對中国持正面看法","createTime":"2019-11-06T08:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T09:08:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"734b921366176325d1029c968dd65af4bd43b2e4","tid":1696580,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:58:25.000Z","msg":"加拿大卑詩大學周一（4日）公布一份調查顯示，僅29%受訪加拿大人對中國持正面看法，過半數憂慮中國可能發動網絡攻擊。目前中加兩國的外交爭端仍陷於僵局。<br />\n<br />\n該大學於9月26日至10月3日進行網上調查，訪問了1503名加拿大成年人。民調顯示，僅29%受訪者對中國持正面看法，百分比低於兩年前的36%，但高於2月的22%。民調結論指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">「心寒感覺很真實」。</span><br />\n<br />\n民調亦發現，半數受訪者不希望華為在加拿大5G網絡設備供應中扮演主要角色。受訪者愈來愈擔心中國對加拿大國內的影響，特別是擔心網絡攻擊及間諜活動。不過，受訪者仍希望與中國繼續進行商業往來，62%受訪者支持兩國磋商雙邊自由貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n自去年12月加拿大拘捕華為副董事長兼首席財務官孟晚舟以來，兩國關係一直陷入僵局，中國還逮捕了加拿大前外交官康明凱和商人斯帕弗，指控兩人涉間諜活動，其後更限制從加拿大進口肉產品和油菜籽。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20191105/s00004/1572927726961/%e8%aa%bf%e6%9f%a5-%e5%83%8529-%e5%8f%97%e8%a8%aa%e5%8a%a0%e6%8b%bf%e5%a4%a7%e4%ba%ba%e5%b0%8d%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%8c%81%e6%ad%a3%e9%9d%a2%e7%9c%8b%e6%b3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20191105%2Fs00004%2F1572927726961%2F%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e6%259f%25a5-%25e5%2583%258529-%25e5%258f%2597%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e5%258a%25a0%25e6%258b%25bf%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25b0%258d%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%258c%2581%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e9%259d%25a2%25e7%259c%258b%25e6%25b3%2595&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=7e99d93d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20191105%2Fs00004%2F1572927726961%2F%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e6%259f%25a5-%25e5%2583%258529-%25e5%258f%2597%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e5%258a%25a0%25e6%258b%25bf%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25b0%258d%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%258c%2581%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e9%259d%25a2%25e7%259c%258b%25e6%25b3%2595&h=577968aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20191105/s00004/1572927726961/%e8%aa%bf%e6%9f%a5-%e5%83%8529-%e5%8f%97%e8%a8%aa%e5%8a%a0%e6%8b%bf%e5%a4%a7%e4%ba%ba%e5%b0%8d%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%8c%81%e6%ad%a3%e9%9d%a2%e7%9c%8b%e6%b3%95</a>"},{"pid":"cd62f24cdbae6cf9688a6d1c9d6b41bb1e413599","tid":1696580,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先45%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a>"},{"pid":"2389be52a969ad3ff1f8487854a3c4d7d099c699","tid":1696580,"uid":61974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:59:45.000Z","msg":"呢29%應該同中國有生意來往"},{"pid":"8d701f71af5b4175c4b0b5c23e357e598d0c6f88","tid":1696580,"uid":224533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:01:14.000Z","msg":"29%係咪加籍支那人?"},{"pid":"7583695e0f5bda3a0276f697776dc5c3c3ee1145","tid":1696580,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"加拿大都算開放同左膠社會<br />\n<br />\n但7-8成 對中國人反感<br />\n支國人真係要反省<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=